ENTRY            D1091   20260318   20260508   20260508       D151
SUBENT        D1091001   20260318   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                 12         23
TITLE      Measurements of the proton-induced reaction
            155Gd(p,n)155Tb at energies between 7 and 26 MeV with
            highly-enriched 155Gd targets
AUTHOR     (M.Bouteculet, C.-O.Bacri, M.-A.Duval, H.Lefort,
            R.Behal, A.Cassisa, A.Gourgiotis, V.Glagolev,
            A.Guertin, O.Lebeda, X.Ledoux, J.Mrazek, E.Nigron,
            J.-C.Thomas, E.Simeckova)
INSTITUTE  (2FR PAR,3CZRUJF,2FR NTE,2FR GAN,2FR ARN)
           (2FR FR) Autorite de surete nucleaire et de
            radioprotection (ASNR), Fontenay-aux-Roses
REFERENCE  (J,ARI,229,112375,2026)
REL-REF    (R,D1030001,M.Bouteculet+,J,ARI,213,111485,2024)
           The cross section of the 155(p,n)155Tb
SAMPLE     155Gd (>99.0% highly enriched) target.
DETECTOR   (HPGE)
METHOD     (STTA,ACTIV)
MONITOR    (22-TI-0(P,X)23-V-48,,SIG)
DECAY-MON  (23-V-48,15.974D,DG,983.525,0.9998,
                            DG,1312.105,0.982)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information on source of uncertainties.
           . The relative uncertainty of 155Tb production cross
            sections is ~10%
HISTORY    (20260318C) VT
ENDBIB              23
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           26
